\par 
\par \tab This is a global tag that surrounds every gallery page. In a stand-alone 
\par \tab installation's template, this ID should be associated with the <body> 
\par \tab attribute. In an embedded installation, the appropriate div should be
\par \tab placed around the Gallery segment in order to seperate out its 
\par \tab namespace from the rest of the document. e.g. <div id="gallery>
\par 
